reviewText: The DVD comes from Japan (the only production) but even though they are advertising NTSC system, my Blue Ray could not read it. I tried it on other DVD players as well and it did not work. I returned it hoping to get a good copy (not here yet). If you want this to play, make sure you get a multi-region DVD/Blue Ray that has PAL/SECAM and others.
Well produced document of a powefrul fusion concert by an allstar band of virtuosos!
